about.summary: Utilities to represent, visualize, filter, analyse, and summarize time-depth recorder (TDR) data.  Miscellaneous functions for handling location data are also provided.

name: r-divemove
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.4.6" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-divemove
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/diveMove_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/diveMove/diveMove_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 922e40566d61015a0d94fa76b442b4ebb15b1786f49f60e5e1e48dcb95d70888

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-kernsmooth
    - r-geosphere
    - r-quantreg
    - r-unireg
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-kernsmooth
    - r-geosphere
    - r-quantreg
    - r-unireg

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('diveMove')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('diveMove')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/spluque/diveMove
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Utilities to represent, visualize, filter, analyse, and summarize time-depth recorder (TDR) data.  Miscellaneous functions for handling location data are also provided.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - alexetnunes
